<para style="p">A psalm of Asaph.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Surely God is good to Israel,</para>

<para style="q1">to those with a pure heart.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />But as for me, my feet almost slipped;</para>

<para style="q1">my feet almost slipped out from under me</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />because I was envious of the arrogant</para>

<para style="q1">when I saw the prosperity of the wicked.</para>
